comments.body:
@mtrmac OK I think this is ready from my side.
I left some pointers in the last commit on how to make the completion experience better. For reference here are the podman completion functions: https://github.com/containers/podman/blob/main/cmd/podman/common/completion.go

If skopeo has a format flag which accepts go templates we could move the `AutocompleteFormat()` function to c/common so that skopeo can use this functionality as well.
